<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Monitoring System Error</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .alert {
            background-color: #ffebee;
            border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .error-details {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 10px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Monitoring System Error</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="alert">
        <strong>Error:</strong> A monitoring system component has encountered an error.
    </div>
    
    <div>
        <h2>Error Details</h2>
        <p><strong>Component:</strong> {{component}}</p>
        <p><strong>Timestamp:</strong> {{timestamp}}</p>
        <p><strong>Error Message:</strong></p>
        <div class="error-details">
            {{errorMessage}}
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <p>Please investigate this issue to ensure proper monitoring system operation.</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message from the Vana Relay Service monitoring system.</p>
        <p>Timestamp: {{timestamp}}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 